n generated (fork a process if this doesn't suit you).  -- NOTE: Both frequency and duration are APPROXIMATE.  END.--LOGTime: 11-Aug-81 10:06:23	By: AWL         Created LOG.  Merged in SoundGenerator functionality. Added SetCursorPosition while   making cursor read-only.